@startuml
title Apply/Preview merge-сценарии для всех MergeStrategy

actor Client
participant "Demo Controller" as C
participant "DttDemoService" as S
participant "DeviceTemplateLibraryFacade" as F
participant "TemplateAssemblyService" as A

== PREVIEW ==
Client -> C: POST /preview (branch/profile)
C -> S: preview...(...)
S -> F: previewProfileImportView(...) / previewBranchImportView(...)
F -> A: preview... + compute...Preview(...)
F --> S: *PreviewView (json/counts/diagnostics)
S --> C: DTO preview response
C --> Client: 200 OK + preview JSON + computations

== APPLY ==
Client -> C: POST /import (branch/profile)
C -> S: import...(...)
S -> F: assemble...ApplyView(...)
F -> A: assemble...
F -> A: compute...Preview(...)
F --> S: *ApplyView (json/counts/diagnostics)
S --> C: DTO apply response
C --> Client: 200 OK + applied JSON + diagnostics

== MERGE (existing branch JSON) ==
Client -> C: POST /import/existing-branch
C -> S: importDttSetToExistingBranch(...)
S -> F: mergeIntoExistingBranchJsonApplyView(...)
F -> A: assemble incoming branch
F -> F: mergeBranchEquipment(existing, incoming, strategy)
alt FAIL_IF_EXISTS
  F --> S: conflict error
else REPLACE
  F --> S: existing replaced by incoming
else MERGE_NON_NULLS
  F --> S: non-null incoming overlays existing
else MERGE_PRESERVE_EXISTING
  F --> S: existing fields preserved
else CREATE_COPY_WITH_SUFFIX
  F --> S: conflicting type copied with suffix
end
S --> C: merge result / error
C --> Client: HTTP result

@enduml
